text:
Learn about the fascinating events leading to the end of the Second World War in the current issue of WM. 

WM features historical insights, compelling personal stories from veterans, and goes behind-the-scenes at the Memorial. 

Subscribe today: http://shop.awm.gov.au

Historian Dr Kristen Alexander is visiting to discuss her book 'Kriegies: The Australian Airmen of Stalag Luft III', sharing the experiences of the 345 Australian airmen incarcerated at the POW Camp. 

When: Wednesday, 14 May 2025 @ 12.30pm
More info: https://trybooking.com/events/landing/1389553…
